			<p class="">Kultiv8 Consulting is your preparation and career coaching partner, founded in 2018 with a focus on personal growth through innovation.</p>

			<p> With roughly over 50% of recent graduates unemployed or underemployed, our mission is to close that gap by offering guidance and coaching services that will increase the likelihood of securing employment. With our 7 years of HR and recruitment and having conducted <span>600+</span> candidate and client interviews; we aim to dispense all that knowledge to newly qualified and experienced professionals.</p>

